---
title: Hearty Black Bean & Poblano Soup with Blue Corn Tortilla Chips, Monterey Jack & Lime Sour Cream
description: Soup-er supper alert! Just one spoonful of this hearty, richly-spiced soup will warm you from the inside out. Black beans simmer with a bounty of Southwest spices, sautéed onion, and smoky poblano until thickened. The soup’s then spooned into bowls and loaded up with all the fixin’s: lime sour cream, Monterey Jack cheese, and cilantro leaves, plus blue corn tortilla chips on the side for dipping. It doesn’t get much better than this, folks.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hearty-black-bean-poblano-soup-4c48fe26.jpg
